    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pieced quilts composed of blocks divided by two horizontal and two vertical seams into a grid of nine major areas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000004131/Brackman, comp., Encyclopedia of Pieced Quilt Patterns (1979)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Colchas a pedazos compuestas de bloques divididos por una costura principal horizontal y por una costura principal vertical para formar una cuadrícula de nueve cuadrados de igual o casi idéntico tamaño.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Patchwork quilts bestaande uit blokken die door twee horizontale en twee verticale naden in negen velden worden verdeeld. Geen Nederlands equivalent.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
